title: The Shadow Queen (World of Hetar #5)  by Bertrice Small EPUB EN
description:
Mourn me but briefly.Then find your
destiny, Lara, my love, my life.

Now let me go.

With those words, the spirit of Magnus Hauk, Dominus
of Terah, leaves his body--and thus the fate of a
nation rests upon the faerie woman Lara's shoulders.

While Lara's son Prince Taj is well loved by the people
of Terah, he is too young to rule, and Lara must obey
Magnus's dying command and govern in his stead.
Thankfully, she has a powerful ally in Prince Kaliq of
the Shadows, though never was there a more seductive
friend or foe. Yet some in Terah still believe that a
female must never wear the crown...and Lara and her
daughters will face old enemies who escaped the wrath
of Magnus but are not yet finished with their
schemes for power and revenge.
